\b \cf0 Game\
\pard\pardeftab720\ri-2160\ql\qnatural

\i\b0 \cf0 Show Equipment
\i0 : Shows everything you are wearing, along with the slot it occupies and its power. If nothing is equipped in a particular slot, this will be indicated. This command is only available while solving a World.\
\pard\pardeftab720\ri0

\i \cf0 Show Item Inventory\'85
\i0 : Shows all combat usable Items you are carrying. This command is only available while solving a World.\
\pard\pardeftab720\ri0\ql\qnatural

\i \cf0 Show Object Inventory...
\i0 : Shows all other Items you are carrying. This command is only available while solving a World.\
\pard\pardeftab720\ri0

\i \cf0 Use an Item...
\i0 : Allows using anything you\'92re carrying that can be explicitly used. This command is only available while solving a World.\
\pard\pardeftab720\ri-2160\ql\qnatural
\cf0 Pick Leader...: Choose a new leader from the characters in your Party. The leader is who will buy and sell stuff from shops, and whose stats will be displayed in the right pane when not in battle.\

\b Battle
\b0\fs24 \

\i\fs28 Cast Spell
\i0 : Prompts for a spell to cast, then a target, then casts the selected spell on the selected target. This command is available only while engaged in battle.\

\i Use an Item
\i0 : Prompts for an item to use, then a target, then uses the selected item on the selected target. This command is available only while engaged in battle.\

\i Steal Stuff
\i0 : Attempt to steal Gold from an adjacent hostile creature. This command is available only while engaged in battle.\

\i Drain MP
\i0 : Attempt to drain MP from an adjacent hostile creature. Any MP drained is given to the drainer. This command is available only while engaged in battle.\

\i End Turn
\i0 : Ends your turn. This command is available only while engaged in battle.\
\pard\pardeftab720\ri0

